comment_text:
&quot;I&#39;m intellectually superior to you.&quot;

-- John Green


Wow, that does have a nice ring to it, now that you mention it... *rubs chin*

It&#39;s not about any sub-par information that may have been shared.
It&#39;s that John basically said, &quot;Here, you want me to talk about battles?  Then sit here for ten minutes while I name battles but don&#39;t actually discuss what was important about them, adding in snarky little comments about how little this matters to me and how intellectually superior I am compared to you.&quot;
Not cool.
